\c 10
\s Tora naJairi
\p
\v 1 Shure kwaAbhimereki kwakamuka Tora mwanakomana waPua mwanakomana waDhodho murume waIsasikari kuponesa Israeri; iye waigara paShamiri panyika yemakomo yaEfuremu\x + Josh. 24.33.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino iye wakatonga Israeri makore makumi maviri nematatu, ndokufa; ndokuvigwa paShamiri.
\p
\v 3 Zvino shure kwake kwakamuka Jairi muGiriyadhi ndokutonga Israeri makore makumi maviri nemaviri.
\v 4 Zvino waiva nevanakomana makumi matatu vaitasva makumi matatu evana vembongoro\x + 5.10.\x*, uye vaiva nemaguta makumi matatu anonzi Havhori-Jairi kusvika nhasi\x + Det. 3.14.\x*, ari munyika yeGiriyadhi.
\v 5 Jairi ndokufa, ndokuvigwa paKamoni.
\s VaIsraeri vanotambudzwa neVaFirisitia neVaAmori
\p
\v 6 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakaitazve chakaipa pameso aJehovha\x + 2.11; 3.7; 4.1; 6.1; 13.1.\x*, ndokushumira vana Bhaari nevaAshitaroti\x + 2.13.\x* nevamwari vaSiriya nevamwari vaSidhoni\x + 1 Madz. 11.5,7,33. 2 Madz. 23.13.\x* nevamwari vaMoabhu nevamwari vevana vaAmoni nevamwari veVaFirisitia\x + 16.23.\x*; ndokusiya Jehovha\x + 10.10,13. Det. 31.16.\x*, uye havana kumushumira.
\v 7 Zvino kutsamwa kwaJehovha kwakapfutira Israeri, iye ndokuvatengesa muruoko rweVaFirisitia\x + Det. 32.30.\x* nemuruoko rwevana vaAmoni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino gore iro ivo\x + Eki. 15.6.\x* vakanetsa nekumanikidza vana vaIsraeri\x + 10.5.\x*, makore gumi nemasere, vose vana vaIsraeri vaiva mhiri kwaJoridhani munyika yeVaAmori, yaiva muGiriyadhi.
\v 9 Uye vana vaAmoni vakayambuka Joridhani kuti varwe kunyange naJudha\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x* uye naBhenjamini uye neimba yaEfuremu; naizvozvo Israeri wakamanikidzika\x + 2.15.\x* kwazvo.
\p
\v 10 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakachema kuna Jehovha\x + 3.9.\x* vachiti: Takatadza kwamuri, uye nokuti takasiya Mwari wedu\x + 10.10,13. Det. 31.16.\x* ndokushumira vana Bhaari.
\v 11 Jehovha ndokuti kuvana vaIsraeri: Ha\add ndi\add*na \add kukuponesai\add* here paVaEgipita\x + Eki. 14.30.\x* nekuVaAmori\x + Num.. 21.21,22,23,24,33,34,35.\x* nekuvana vaAmoni\x + 3.13.\x* nekuVaFirisitia\x + 3.13.\x*?
\v 12 VaSidhoniwo neVaAmareki\x + 3.13; 5.14; 6.3.\x* neVaMaoni\x + 2 Makor. 26.7. 1 Makor. 4.41.\x* vakakumanikidzai\x + Map. 106.42,43.\x*. Zvino mukachema kwandiri; ini ndokukusunungurai paruoko rwavo.
\v 13 Zvakadaro imwi makandisiya\x + 10.6. Det. 32.15. Jer. 2.13.\x* ndokushumira vamwe vamwari; naizvozvo handina kukuponesaizve.
\v 14 Endai munochema kuna vamwari vamakasarudza\x + Det. 32.37,38.\x*; ivo ngavakuponesei panguva yedambudziko renyu.
\p
\v 15 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakati kuna Jehovha: Takatadza; imwi tiitirei zvichienderana nezvose zvakanaka pameso enyu; koga tisunungurei henyu nhasi.
\v 16 Zvino vakabvisa vamwari vevatorwa kubva pakati pavo ndokushumira Jehovha; moyo wake\x + 2.18.\x* ndokushungurudzika nedambudziko raIsraeri\x + Isa. 63.9.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino kwakadanirwa pamwe vana vaAmoni, ndokudzika matende paGiriyadhi. Vana vaIsraeri vakaunganawo pamwe, ndokudzika matende paMizipa\x + 11.11,29. Josh. 11.3.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino vanhu, machinda aGiriyadhi vakati umwe kune umwe: Ndiani munhu achatanga kurwa nevana vaAmoni? Achava musoro pavagari vose veGiriyadhi\x + 11.5,6,8,11.\x*.